<eesti>Kinnituse v&auml;ljastamine </eesti>
<inglise>Issue of approval </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kinnituse v&auml;ljastab Sideamet. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An approval shall be issued by the Communications Board. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Sideamet v&auml;ljastab raadiosagedusala kasutuse n&otilde;uetele vastavuse kinnituse mitte hiljem kui nelja n&auml;dala jooksul p&auml;rast kinnituse taotlemiseks vajalike dokumentide saamist. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Communications Board shall issue an approval of conformity of the use of a radio frequency band not later than within four weeks after receipt of the documents necessary for applying for approval. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Sideameti poolt v&auml;ljastatav k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas toodud vormi kohane kinnitus sisaldab v&auml;hemalt j&auml;rgmisi andmeid: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) An approval issued by the Communications Board in compliance with the format specified in the Annex to this Regulation shall contain at least the following information: </inglise>
<eesti>1) tootja v&otilde;i tootja ja tarnija nimi ning aadress; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the name(s) and address(es) of the manufacturer or the manufacturer and the supplier; </inglise>
<eesti>2) raadiosaateseadme nimi ja t&uuml;&uuml;p; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the name and type of the radio transmission equipment; </inglise>
<eesti>3) raadiosaateseadme tehnilised andmed: sagedus, raadiosageduskanali samm, modulatsioonit&uuml;&uuml;p ja v&auml;ljundv&otilde;imsus; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the technical data concerning the radio transmission equipment: the frequency band, channel spacing, type of modulation and RF-power; </inglise>
<eesti>4) raadiosaateseadme kasutamise n&otilde;uded. </eesti>
<inglise>4) the requirements for the use of the radio transmission equipment. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Juhul kui kinnitust ei ole v&otilde;imalik v&auml;ljastada, teatab Sideamet sellest taotlejale kirjalikult, tuues &auml;ra keeldumise p&otilde;hjuse. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If an approval cannot be issued, the Communications Board shall notify the applicant in writing of the refusal to issue an approval and shall indicate the reason for refusal. </inglise>
